|----------|--------|----------|-------|
| content | 0.18 | 6 | |
| language | 0.18 | 8 | |
| style | 0.18 | 6 | |
| communication | 0.13 | 4 | |
| filler | 0.08 | 4 | |
| structure | 0.15 | 5 | |
| viral-hook | 0.10 | 9 | score-only (no rewrite) |
